        <div class="foreground how-to-media-large"><div class="how-to-heading">
            
          <h2 id="how-to-merge-pdf-files-online" class="heading-l">How to merge PDF files online</h2><p>With the merge PDF tool from Adobe Acrobat, you can combine multiple PDF documents into one file for free online. Now it’s easy to merge separate PDFs, organize pages in your document, and create a single, shareable PDF without installing software.<br><br>Learn how to combine multiple PDF files into one with these easy steps:</p></div><div class="how-to-media how-to-media-large"><span class="modal-img-link"><picture>
                  <source type="image/webp" srcset="/acrobat/online/media_1ae354d8b7b963af98bab4a16e677e185a54545aa.png?width=2000&amp;format=webply&amp;optimize=medium" media="(min-width: 600px)">
