                  <img loading="lazy" alt="Play video: How to merge PDFs" src="/acrobat/online/media_1ae354d8b7b963af98bab4a16e677e185a54545aa.png?width=750&amp;format=png&amp;optimize=medium" width="912" height="642" role="none">
                </picture><a href="/acrobat/online/merge-pdf/" class="modal link-block image-link btn-medium consonant-play-btn" data-modal-path="/dc-shared/fragments/modals/videos/frictionless/how-to-merge-pdfs" data-modal-hash="#video" role="button" aria-label="Play Play video: How to merge PDFs" data-block-status="loaded" daa-ll="Play Play video How -1--How to merge PDF fil"><div class="play-icon-container"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="42" viewBox="0 0 40 42" fill="none" class="play-icon" aria-hidden="true">
