                      </svg></div></a></span></div><ol><li><div>Click the <strong>Select files</strong> button above, or drag and drop files into the drop zone.</div></li><li><div>Select the files you want to merge using the Acrobat PDF combiner tool.</div></li><li><div>Reorder the files if needed.</div></li><li><div>Click <strong>Merge files</strong>.</div></li><li><div>Download your merged file or sign in to share it with a link.</div></li></ol></div></div>
